# CODEOWNERS — PR-time governance complement to local protected-path enforcement
#
# GitHub evaluates CODEOWNERS on every pull request and requires approval
# from the listed owners before the PR can merge (when branch protection
# is configured — see docs/branch-protection.md).
#
# Paths mirror the orchestrator's local protected-path enforcement
# (see docs/orchestrator-work-and-isolation.md § Protected Control-Plane
# Paths) so that the same files guarded at task-completion time are also
# guarded at PR-merge time.
#
# Replace @anthropic-team/orchestrator-maintainers with your actual
# GitHub team or user handles.

# ── Orchestrator runtime and control plane ──────────────────────────
